OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum urges government to
OL,4,Cintroduce mindfulness to all schools
OL,6,FMs Ghey said: "Before Brianna was
OL,7,Fmurdered she really struggled with her
OL,8,Fmental health.
OL,10,F"She had an eating disorder, she was
OL,11,Fself harming and she had anxiety to
OL,12,Fthe point where she was refusing to
OL,13,Fcome to school."
OL,15,FBrianna , 16, was killed in a
OL,16,F"frenzied and ferocious" attack after
OL,17,Fbeing lured to Culcheth Linear Park,
OL,18,Fin Warrington, on 11 February 2023.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
