OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum urges government to
OL,4,Cintroduce mindfulness to all schools
OL,6,FMs Ghey has been raising money to
OL,7,Fbring mindfulness into schools across
OL,8,Fthe country through her campaign,
OL,9,FPeace in Mind.
OL,11,FIt had already been introduced at
OL,12,FBrianna's school, Birchwood Community
OL,13,FHigh School.
OL,15,FMindfulness is a calming technique
OL,16,F-the charity Mind says it involves
OL,17,Fnoticing what is happening in the
OL,18,Fpresent moment, without judgment.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
