OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum urges government to
OL,4,Cintroduce mindfulness to all schools
OL,6,FMs Ghey said: "I have practised
OL,7,Fmindfulness for ten years now and I
OL,8,Fknow how much mindfulness helps with
OL,9,Fmental resilience, empathy and self
OL,10,Fcompassion.
OL,12,F"After Brianna's death I realised so
OL,13,Fmany other young people are really
OL,14,Fstruggling and I think its really
OL,15,Fimportant to get mindfulness into
OL,16,Fschools at a young age so we can help
OL,17,Fyoung people with their mental health
OL,18,Fand also build empathy and unity
OL,19,Fwithin our communities."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
