OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum urges government to
OL,4,Cintroduce mindfulness to all schools
OL,6,F"I know that mindfulness has enabled
OL,7,Fme to build a level of mental
OL,8,Fresilience and I liken it to mental
OL,9,Fstrength just as if you were to go to
OL,10,Fthe gym and build muscle through
OL,11,Fresistance training. It's the same
OL,12,Fkind of thing, but for your mind," she
OL,13,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
