OL,3,CBrianna Ghey's mum urges government to
OL,4,Cintroduce mindfulness to all schools
OL,6,F"In the past I have struggled with
OL,7,Fmental health issues and I know if
OL,8,Fwhat happened to Brianna happened to
OL,9,Fme then, before I had the mindfulness
OL,10,Ftools in place, then it would have
OL,11,Fbeen a completely different story and
OL,12,FI really do believe that mindfulness
OL,13,Fsaved me."
OL,15,FTo date the peace and mind campaign
OL,16,Fset up in Brianna's memory has raised
OL,17,Fmore than a hundred thousand pounds -
OL,18,Fenough to train a mindfulness teacher
OL,19,Fin every school in Warrington.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
